{"tid":557922,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得籃球係一種點樣既運動？","createTime":"2018-02-11T19:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T12:04:10.000Z","uid":158541,"like":30,"dislike":119,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7a6f9ddfb81b323c37af787041edf7fd181b1c","tid":557922,"uid":158541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T19:35:40.000Z","msg":"就算你唔打籃球，都可以幫手投下，我想知籃球係大家心目中係種點樣既運動。<br />\n<br />\n努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地高過我 我就練爆發力 跳高D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大隻過我 我就要練得更靈活  快到可以過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天賦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本基因決定一切 你再練都有極限 你睇下D高佬 唔洗跳都block到你 你就跳到死都 掂唔到佢個ball一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f249ad7f329974cc6fee6aa5912d86a3dfbc9c43","tid":557922,"uid":124414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T19:37:22.000Z","msg":"得分 / 助攻 果種感覺都幾正"},{"pid":"79f5ab905b29be83ac66ae702f4771e84727288c","tid":557922,"uid":158541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T19:38:20.000Z","msg":"如果可以 大家可以講下自己既原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110fecbbcb29428ae2f1128993913cf5331c1d5f","tid":557922,"uid":555,"like":46,"dislike":10,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T19:44:56.000Z","msg":"運動？係咪有咩誤會"},{"pid":"ac284eff2351c48373cbaf9ae9db4918dd97858f","tid":557922,"uid":124941,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T19:52:10.000Z","msg":"根本所有運動都講天賦"},{"pid":"580f3a20f83bdfcf602a98fd92a3fea6f750d645","tid":557922,"uid":62277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T20:28:36.000Z","msg":"爆發力,彈跳力都係先天多於努力<br />\n<br />\n高真係玩曬<br />\n如果同你對位嗰個高你10cm<br />\n佢跟本唔洗用技術過你<br />\n如果有返咁上下準<br />\n球球喺你面前顏射你都吹唔脹<br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n就算你係好準<br />\n佢喺你面前舉起手都好干擾<br />\n命中率大減<br />\n<br />\n就算打外線高度一樣咁重要<br />\n睇返而家nba<br />\n1號位代表人物wb,curry,irving<br />\n3號位代表人物kd,james,kl<br />\n喺同位置球員中都算高<br />\n<br />\n所以真係好尊敬it<br />\n咁矮都可以有咁既得分能力<br />\n不過我覺得高度亦係佢唔可以保持長期命中率穩定既原因<br />\nbtw,以佢身高又射咁多外圍<br />\n有43,4%已好唔錯"},{"pid":"152e8deffb4de8fe7cc12485665bea25d1d118c9","tid":557922,"uid":80830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"580f3a20f83bdfcf602a98fd92a3fea6f750d645","tid":557922,"uid":62277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T20:28:36.000Z","msg":"爆發力,彈跳力都係先天多於努力<br />\n<br />\n高真係玩曬<br />\n如果同你對位嗰個高你10cm<br />\n佢跟本唔洗用技術過你<br />\n如果有返咁上下準<br />\n球球喺你面前顏射你都吹唔脹<br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n就算你係好準<br />\n佢喺你面前舉起手都好干擾<br />\n命中率大減<br />\n<br />\n就算打外線高度一樣咁重要<br />\n睇返而家nba<br />\n1號位代表人物wb,curry,irving<br />\n3號位代表人物kd,james,kl<br />\n喺同位置球員中都算高<br />\n<br />\n所以真係好尊敬it<br />\n咁矮都可以有咁既得分能力<br />\n不過我覺得高度亦係佢唔可以保持長期命中率穩定既原因<br />\nbtw,以佢身高又射咁多外圍<br />\n有43,4%已好唔錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T20:35:19.000Z","msg":"可愛2米01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca905342fbee0378209024dd885927f87ca59d3e","tid":557922,"uid":136900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T20:45:37.000Z","msg":"係 黑子的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b683e9041a04faedbbc4d0e3a6aa2336c140d7b","tid":557922,"uid":120070,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T20:50:26.000Z","msg":"猩猩先會做既運動"},{"pid":"bf2f30be3c305ecef9772b4fbc01bd8e471f9ea0","tid":557922,"uid":158541,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T20:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>猩猩先會做既運動</blockquote><br />\n其實有道理 如果用NBA 同我地比 籃球真係一種比白人 甚至黑人玩既運動"},{"pid":"6f729aa20b859df020e1918e04987606a2927fa2","tid":557922,"uid":89134,"like